<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1437,1370,2007]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3311767437" collectionCode="MZSP" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" specimenCount="1">
The second author was unable to locate the 
<typeStatus box="[651,699,1371,1395]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">type</typeStatus>
series of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Duda" box="[811,1061,1371,1395]" class="Insecta" family="Sphaeroceridae" genus="Aptilotella" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="borgmeieri">
<emphasis box="[811,1061,1371,1395]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Aptilotella borgmeieri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
at 
<collectionCode box="[1098,1172,1370,1395]" country="Brazil" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/9yp6-zxp9" name="Sao Paulo, Museu de Zoologia da Universidade de Sao Paulo" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="Museum">MZSP</collectionCode>
. Since these specimens have apparently been lost, the following redescription of the male is adapted from Duda’s original German description in 1924
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
